---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import StepPattern from '../components/ornament/StepPattern.astro';
import ArcBracket from '../components/ornament/ArcBracket.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Coaching" description="Zen coaching, meditation facilitation, and grounded inner work.">
  <main class="container">
    <figure class="page-hero" aria-hidden="true">
      <img src="/heroes/coaching.webp?v=sketch" srcset="/heroes/coaching-sm.webp?v=sketch 800w, /heroes/coaching.webp?v=sketch 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 860px" width="1600" height="900" alt="" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high" />
    </figure>

    <section class="hero">
      <p class="eyebrow">Zen coaching session</p>
      <h1>Grounded inquiry for people who are done performing clarity.</h1>
      <p class="lede">A 60-minute inquiry session — grounding, honest dialogue, and space to let your own seeing return.</p>
      <p class="launch-note"><strong>Launch offer:</strong> 350 SEK per session (half off the standard 700 SEK) while I complete my certification — through 31 August 2026.</p>
      <div class="cta-group">
        <a class="cta cta-primary" href="https://calendar.proton.me/bookings#IGkV7dEHWdtLywfZTLXP2KivEYKrhBRYtxTLf8IdkzI=" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Book a session</a>
        <a class="cta cta-secondary" href="mailto:dennis@dyallo.se?subject=Free%2020-min%20intro%20call">First time? Book a free 20-min intro call</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="sections">
      <section>
        <h2>What it is</h2>
        <p>Collaborative dialogue exploring how stories live in your body. We move from understanding to embodied awareness to capable action. You already have what you need — we create space to access it.</p>
        <p>Each session begins with grounding meditation and invitation to speak from the heart — slowly enough to feel your words land.</p>
      </section>

      <div class="pullquote" aria-hidden="false">
        <ArcBracket />
        <blockquote>These sessions are about <em>knocking the door</em>, not complete therapeutic arcs.</blockquote>
        <p class="pullquote-note">Integration support and follow-up available.</p>
      </div>

      <section>
        <h2>Who this is for</h2>
        <p>People navigating change, creative blocks, relational friction, spiritual bypassing, or the quiet sense that the old operating system is no longer honest.</p>
        <p>It fits best if you want directness without theater: no guru posture, no productivity cosplay, no promise that one session will turn your life into a diagram.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Pricing</h2>
        <p><strong>350 SEK per 60-minute session</strong> during my launch — half off the standard 700 SEK. I'm running this introductory rate while I complete my certification and gather feedback, through 31 August 2026.</p>
        <p>First-time clients can start with a free 20-minute intro call to feel the fit before booking.</p>
        <p>Sessions are held online (the default), in person at my place, or at a meeting place of your choice (limited availability).</p>
      </section>

      <div class="mid-ornament" aria-hidden="true"><StepPattern /></div>

      <section>
        <h2>Training and approach</h2>
        <p>I've completed the full year-long Zen Coaching training — all five modules — and am now working toward full certification. My practice roots run through Vipassana meditation, yoga, contemplative traditions, men's circles, movement work, and retreat facilitation.</p>
        <p>The approach is warm and direct. Less guru, more honest mirror. I care about sovereignty: helping you return to your own seeing instead of becoming dependent on mine.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>FAQs</h2>
        <div class="faq">
          <h3>Is this therapy?</h3>
          <p>No. Coaching can be deeply useful, but it is not clinical treatment, diagnosis, or a substitute for therapy.</p>
          <h3>Do I need meditation experience?</h3>
          <p>No. A willingness to pay attention honestly is more important than any formal practice history.</p>
          <h3>Can sessions be remote?</h3>
          <p>Yes. Online is the default. In person is also possible at my place, or at a meeting place of your choice (limited availability).</p>
          <h3>How long is a session?</h3>
          <p>60 minutes. A free 20-minute intro call is available for first-time clients to find your fit.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>Email <a href="mailto:dennis@dyallo.se">dennis@dyallo.se</a> with a few lines about what you are navigating and what made you reach out now.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>

  <style>
    .container { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: var(--space-3xl) var(--space-lg); }
    .hero { max-width: 720px; margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl); }
    .eyebrow { color: var(--gold); font-size: var(--type-small); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); }
    h1 { font-size: var(--type-h1); margin-bottom: var(--space-md); }
    .hero p, section p { color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.65; }
    .lede { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1.12rem; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: var(--space-md); }
    .launch-note { color: var(--ink); background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-left: 3px solid var(--gold); border-radius: var(--radius-sm); padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-md); margin-bottom: var(--space-lg); font-size: var(--type-small); }
    .launch-note strong { color: var(--gold); }
    .cta-group { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: var(--space-md); align-items: center; margin-top: var(--space-md); }
    .cta { display: inline-flex; padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-lg); border-radius: var(--radius-sm); text-decoration: none; transition: opacity var(--transition-fast), background var(--transition-fast); }
    .cta-primary { background: var(--primary); color: var(--bg); font-weight: 600; }
    .cta-primary:hover { opacity: 0.88; }
    .cta-secondary { color: var(--muted); border: 1px solid var(--border); font-size: var(--type-small); padding: 0.45rem 0.85rem; }
    .cta-secondary:hover { border-color: var(--primary); color: var(--ink); }
    .pullquote { margin: var(--space-2xl) auto; max-width: 640px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-sm); color: var(--gold); text-align: center; }
    .pullquote blockquote { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1.4rem; line-height: 1.5; color: var(--ink); margin: 0; }
    .pullquote blockquote em { color: var(--primary); font-style: italic; }
    .pullquote-note { color: var(--muted); font-size: var(--type-small); margin: 0; }
    .sections { display: grid; gap: var(--space-xl); }
    section:not(.hero) { padding-bottom: var(--space-xl); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
    h2 { font-size: var(--type-h3); margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); }
    h3 { font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: var(--type-body); font-weight: 600; margin-top: var(--space-md); margin-bottom: var(--space-xs); }
    p + p { margin-top: var(--space-sm); }
    .mid-ornament { display: flex; justify-content: center; margin: var(--space-2xl) 0; color: var(--gold); }
    @media (max-width: 768px) { h1 { font-size: var(--type-h2); } }
    .page-hero { margin: 0 0 var(--space-2xl); border-radius: var(--radius-md); overflow: hidden; aspect-ratio: 16 / 9; background: var(--surface); }
    .page-hero img { display: block; width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }

  </style>
</BaseLayout>
